+  CPU    |       |VPROC  |PROCALT|PROCMIG|PROCTRL|       | |SCHED. |       |
+  PROCESS|     08|     09|     10|     11|     12|     13| |     14|     15|
+  -------+-------+-------+-------+-------+-------+-------+ +-------+-------+
+  MEMORY |       |       |       |       |       |       | |SWAP   |       |
+         |     16|     17|     18|     19|     20|     21| |     22|     23|
+  -------+-------+-------+-------+-------+-------+-------+ +-------+-------+
